SUMMARY:NBHC — Fixed Income Investor Call
DESCRIPTION:Fixed income investor call. Piper Sandler coordinating logistics.\nIssuer: NATL BANK HOLDINGS (NBHC)\n\nDeal context:\nNational Bank Holdings has mandated Piper Sandler to organize fixed income investor calls on February 5-6\, 2026\, ahead of a potential SEC-registered subordinated notes offering from the holding company. The deal is subject to market conditions and carries expected Moody's ratings of Baa2 with a negative outlook\, positioning this as an investment grade transaction. No specific size or tenor has been disclosed at this mandate stage.
LOCATION:Conference Call
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR